I’ll quickly verify the rover model and key nodes again so I can tell you exactly which novelty ideas are already present versus missing.

Read [](file:///home/pes2ug23cs383/mar_project/space-rover/src/space_rover/urdf/rover.urdf.xacro)

Read [](file:///home/pes2ug23cs383/mar_project/space-rover/src/space_rover/urdf/rover.gazebo)

Read [](file:///home/pes2ug23cs383/mar_project/space-rover/src/space_rover/space_rover/navigation/obstacle_avoidance.py)

